{"tid":184630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滿16歲最重判監8年","createTime":"2017-04-03T02:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T08:43:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da273b72d88c9c251689770f09934ef932f2201a","tid":184630,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19978643&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19978643%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170403&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ad783832\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19978643%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170403&h=844eadb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19978643&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170403</a><br />\n<br />\n滿16歲最重判監8年<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】涉在名校更衣室偷拍同學的7名男學生年僅15至16歲，大律師陸偉雄警告他們涉犯下嚴重罪行，恐前途盡毀。因學生若以隱藏鏡頭在更衣室偷拍，除了會觸犯最高可判監5年的有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦罪名；若有未成年女學生在更衣室被偷拍裸體，偷拍學生更可能被控以可判監8年及罰款200萬的製作兒童色情物品重罪。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄呼籲青少年切勿以身試法。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n無偷拍只藏影片亦犯法<br />\n<br />\n陸偉雄呼籲青少年切勿以身試法，因縱然疑犯在名校內成績如何優異，若有案底，出獄後恐無法成為專業人士如醫生或律師，亦難以獲聘為公務員。陸補充，案中15歲被捕人因未成年可在兒童法庭受審，罪成後法官尚有機會判以感化、入住兒童院等較輕處分；但滿16歲被捕人則料需在成人法庭受審，及有機會被判以長期監禁。<br />\n<br />\n陸警告學生切勿以為在更衣室偷拍同學是小事，因事件嚴重侵犯受害者的私隱，法官很可能會重判至接近法例容許的上限，因若偷拍者不論有意或無意把學生裸體影片在網上公開，對事主造成的傷害將無可挽回；另外其他學生即使無份偷拍，但假如有人私下儲存未成年同學的偷拍裸體影片，一樣可被控以管有兒童色情物品罪名，最高可判監5年。<br />\n■記者陳志偉<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n直資名校人才輩出<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;4小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n校內更衣室裝偷拍鏡頭聖士提反書院　七男生被捕<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;4小時前"},{"pid":"9e2110bc02a323eaaf83f8c8b2444c1b78474e18","tid":184630,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:45:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76127ccf269a486d9077c661fe7d227f105a62c0","tid":184630,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>判終生啦呢d變態性罪犯</blockquote><br />\n有錢仔 名校 成績優異 父母公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6b52291f3ead8811652976c5461f7d074f00a8","tid":184630,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>判終生啦呢d變態性罪犯</blockquote><br />\n有錢仔 名校 成績優異 父母公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果父母係高級警犬， Sorry Sir / Madam 只係一場誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26fed7099aa4c139f83c56b02f856cecc52c1c0","tid":184630,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T03:02:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>判終生啦呢d變態性罪犯</blockquote><br />\n有錢仔 名校 成績優異 父母公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n父母公務員點算有錢仔呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n司長級都係得幾十萬一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聖士提反果班有錢佬會搵咁少?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe456d955e0f505fdd67258b8170a8bd513673b","tid":184630,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>判終生啦呢d變態性罪犯</blockquote><br />\n有錢仔 名校 成績優異 父母公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n父母公務員點算有錢仔呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n司長級都係得幾十萬一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聖士提反果班有錢佬會搵咁少?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲差天主教徒"},{"pid":"63870b155112af1dbb81f9ca